{"tid":923940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"位元堂fb公然侵犯版權","createTime":"2018-12-01T16:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T16:41:06.000Z","uid":193209,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b76a02542cc0273efabf220e4ea430f803e1c19","tid":923940,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"首先講兩句廢話先，二次創作係咪侵權一直有好多爭議<br />\n呢一點我唔打算喺到爭論<br />\n我自己就支持用二次創作去諷刺社會<br />\n簡單啲嚟講，支持二次創作嘅人都公認有一守則要守<br />\n就係唔可以借二次創作之名去做商業活動，因為呢點係會影響版權人嘅利益<br />\n之前有一個香港醬油品牌已經好踩界，二次創作咗咕嚕咕嚕魔法陣<br />\n去幫佢地嘅賣廣告，成班人仲讚佢哋有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢地識玩，從來都無認過係二創（好似係）<br />\n啱啱睇facebook，見到位元堂賣廣告<br />\n心諗做乜9? 矢吹丈都出埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂，你而家唔係二次創作吖，係侵權啊<br />\n有無比版權費啊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahXyJ6D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahXyJ6D.jpg&h=d6e07116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到已經好撚嬲，再睇下啲留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDVAc0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDVAc0K.png&h=fa80a8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得一讚？成個人物一模一樣咁放落去都值得一讚？<br />\n知唔知醜㗎？位元堂留言仲好笑&quot;多謝支持! creative的確諗得好辛苦!&quot;<br />\ncre乞撚嘢ative？公然侵犯版權啊creative<br />\n<br />\n之前講咗，如果佢唔認的話，理論上佢無恥但吹佢唔脹<br />\n但睇下佢講乜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9wGS2m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9wGS2m.png&h=0fb6313c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋話今次到矢吹丈，下次到邊個，佢答&quot;你估吓&quot;<br />\n咁係咪認咗呢個係矢吹丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n至於係咪抄，我做咗張gif，大家自行判斷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNPdJ94.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNPdJ94.gif&h=1487171d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8e3d1467a2eaccf526ba0e6e7854ef64618bed3","tid":923940,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb8e8f688bb12d97ce9aa4b85e434aaeecd4f89","tid":923940,"uid":171124,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"香港係咁架喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}